.description
This cute game has you, the intrepid Peter, following a trail of hearts
through a world of 20 levels, riddled with porcupines and other hazards, to
rescue Daphne, the love of your life that has been kidnapped by the evil
Brutus.  Includes digitized sound and colorful graphics.  New features
include super speed, super jump, rocket pack, and more.  
